            <p class="text-sm">Corn-based ethanol is the mandated additive in gasoline to produce E-85 grade gasoline. The industrial production of ethanol from corn requires separating corn biomass from the ethanol using centrifugal filters such as <a href="/decanter-centrifuge/" class="text-navy font-semibold hover:text-gold transition-colors">decanter centrifuges</a>.</p>
